	\begin{equation}
		\phi(z) \equiv \mu(z) - \nu(z)
	\end{equation}
	where:
	\begin{itemize}
		\item \( \mu(z) \) is a Gaussian sum over normalized CMB TT peaks, representing coherence bursts,
