	Here, \( A_i \) are normalized power amplitudes from the Planck TT spectrum \( D_\ell^{TT} \), and \( z_i = 1100 / (\ell_i + \epsilon) \) maps each multipole to redshift via an acoustic projection consistent with recombination-era causality.
	
